body:
ANNFiD is a tool using Artificial Neural Networks (powered by Encog) to detect types of corrupted files.

The actual page for ANNFiD and my blog is located here, where you can find tutorials and other projects...

If you wish to contribute to the project you are more than welcome...Please c ontact me :) (again, on my web page)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
name: ANNFiD
tagline: ANNFiD Artificial neural network forensic file analyzer
